headline: ADM: Q3 Earnings Snapshot
summary: CHICAGO (AP) — Archer Daniels Midland Co. (ADM) on Tuesday reported third-quarter net income of $108 million. On a per-share basis, the Chicago-based company said it had net income of 22 cents. Earnings, adjusted for asset impairment costs and non-recurring costs, were 92 cents per share.
